casebody.data:
Cara Beth LITTLE, Respondent,
v.
Jamold Bucannon LITTLE, Appellant. WD 81380 CONS WD 81397 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Order filed: May 14, 2019 Malia T. Parnell, Columbia, for Respondent. Jamold Bucannon Little, Appellant Pro-se. Before Division One: Victor C. Howard, Presiding Judge, Lisa White Hardwick, Judge and Gary D. Witt, Judge

ORDER

PER CURIAM:

Jamold Little appeals from the judgment of the trial court modifying custody of the parties' minor children. He raises four points on appeal. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, a memorandum explaining the decision is provided to the parties. The judgment is affirmed. Rule 84.16(b).
